      <title>JBS 称消费者不愿为可持续食品付费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/consumers-unwilling-to-pay-up-for-sustainable-food-jbs-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大肉类公司的高管表示，消费者不愿意为按照更高环境标准生产的食品支付额外费用，这对生产商构成了挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/consumers-unwilling-to-pay-up-for-sustainable-food-jbs-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 21:39:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
